original_title: Manhattan: New Chambers Street - William Street
text:
(1)
20-22 New Chambers Street, south side, between William and Pearl Streets. (New Chambers Street, is arbitrarily set to run east and west).
June 24, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, showing a close up of No. 20.
June 24, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.

ASSUMING STREET TO BE EAST AND WEST.
